data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!! Buyer financing fell through! All certs/inspections complete!   Remarkable mid century modern homestead situated on large lot in Millville! This 4 bedroom 3 full bath home is waiting for its new owner! Offering exceptional charm including tiled foyer, this large 3 bedroom + 4th (in-law suite) down stairs & 3.5 bathrooms has tons of parking, 2 zone AC, full basement, central vacuum system, intercom system along with custom built ins in the workshop, green house and plexiglass breezeway/year round room! Additional features include full basement; handicap accessible features; cedar closet; wood burning fire place & so much more!
